          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">Britain’s Home Office maintains that Harry’s change in royal status and relocation abroad justified a case-by-case approach to dealing with his security. Harry, raising safety concerns for his family and the UK’s importance to his children, feels he was treated differently.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">Harry has been the subject of other recent controversies. Two weeks ago, he <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-10-04-2025-h1-2-resigned-from-sentebale?source=website" target="_blank">resigned from Sentebale</a>, a charity he co-founded, over accusations of bullying and misogyny from one of the key members.</p>
