              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
                    "><strong>In what could be a first of many, Shopify CEO Tobi Lütke told staff that newer hires must be justified by proving AI can’t do the job</strong>. He emphasized AI use as a core job expectation. AI skills will be evaluated during reviews, applying to all employees, including leadership, as Shopify prioritizes AI integration across its operations. Other tech companies are expected to follow suit (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-10-04-2025-br5-10-great-replacement?source=website" target="_blank">great replacement</a>).</p>
